your-app/
├── public/
│   ├── icons/
│   │   └── icon-192.png, icon-512.png
│   ├── manifest.json        ← Web app manifest
│   └── sw.js                ← Service worker
├── next.config.js           ← Enables service worker
├── pages/_document.tsx      ← Injects manifest + icons
├── package.json             ← +PWA plugin
